## üü° MEDIUM PRIORITY: Container Inconsistencies (12+ variations)

### Current Container Patterns Found

| Pattern | Count | Pages Using | Status |
|---------|-------|-------------|--------|
| `maxW="7xl"` | 7 | Orders, Payments, Proposals, etc. | ‚úÖ **Standard** |
| `maxW="6xl"` | 4 | Contractors, Leads, etc. | ‚úÖ **Standard** |
| `maxW="container.xl"` | 1 | GlobalMods | ‚úÖ **Standard** |
| `maxW="5xl"` | 1 | EditCustomer | ‚ö†Ô∏è **Non-standard** |
| `maxW="4xl"` | 1 | Unknown page | ‚ö†Ô∏è **Non-standard** |
| `maxW="3xl"` | 2 | Unknown pages | ‚ö†Ô∏è **Non-standard** |
| `maxW="full"` | 2 | PaymentTest, PaymentResult | ‚ö†Ô∏è **May be intentional** |
| `maxW="800px"` | 2 | Unknown pages | ‚ö†Ô∏è **Non-standard** |
| `maxW="520px"` | 2 | Search boxes | ‚úÖ **Standard for search** |

### Issues:

1. **Non-standard sizes** (3xl, 4xl, 5xl, 800px) - Should use our 3 standard patterns
2. **maxW="full"** on non-test pages - May cause content to be too wide
3. **Pixel values instead of Chakra tokens** - Should use responsive tokens

### Recommendations:

**Convert to Standards**:
- `maxW="5xl"` ‚Üí `maxW="6xl"` (form pages)
- `maxW="4xl"` ‚Üí `maxW="6xl"` (form pages)
- `maxW="3xl"` ‚Üí `maxW="6xl"` (form pages)
- `maxW="800px"` ‚Üí `maxW="container.xl"` (settings)
- Keep `maxW="full"` only for test/result pages

**Estimated time**: 1 hour to standardize all

