- **Why Important**: Admin page with Bootstrap classes that needed conversion
- **Changes Made**:
  - Fixed empty state icons: `<Search size={20} />` ‚Üí `<Users size={48} />`
  - Converted Bootstrap to Chakra: `className="d-none d-md-block"` ‚Üí `<Box display={{ base: 'none', lg: 'block' }}>`
  - Fixed breakpoint: md ‚Üí lg

```jsx
// Before (Bootstrap)
<div className="d-none d-md-block table-wrap">
  <Table>...</Table>
</div>
<div className="settings-mobile-cards d-md-none">
  {/* Mobile cards */}
</div>

// After (Chakra)
<Box display={{ base: 'none', lg: 'block' }} className="table-wrap">
  <Table>...</Table>
</Box>
<Box display={{ base: 'block', lg: 'none' }} className="settings-mobile-cards">
  {/* Mobile cards */}
</Box>
```

